ORM: Active Record

Map rows in a database to instances of a class

model mirrors tables it stores data in
  - model is singular and lowercase (post)
  - table is plural (posts)

Heredoc  <<-ARBITRARY
blah blah
blah
blah blah blah
ARBITRARY

There's a sqlite ruby gem!

If you're interpolating values directly into sql statement you're doing it wrong.  Let the driver do the sanitizing first and then add in the variables (this is where you have the ? in the SQL statement)